texts.content: {"text":"وَمَآ أَدْرَىٰكَ مَا ٱلْقَارِعَةُ ﴿٣﴾","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[0.929411768913269,0.7764706015586853,0.556862771511078]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/KFGQPC Uthman Taha Naskh Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":12.16599178314209,"useLetterColor":true,"range":[0,38]}]}

{"text":"يَوْمَ يَكُونُ ٱلنَّاسُ كَٱلْفَرَاشِ ٱلْمَبْثُوثِ ﴿٤﴾","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[0.929411768913269,0.7764706015586853,0.556862771511078]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/KFGQPC Uthman Taha Naskh Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":12.16599178314209,"useLetterColor":true,"range":[0,53]}]}

{"text":"وَتَكُونُ ٱلْجِبَالُ كَٱلْعِهْنِ ٱلْمَنفُوشِ ﴿٥﴾","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[0.929411768913269,0.7764706015586853,0.556862771511078]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/KFGQPC Uthman Taha Naskh Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":12.16599178314209,"useLetterColor":true,"range":[0,48]}]}

{"text":"فَأَمَّا مَن ثَقُلَتْ مَوَٰزِينُهُۥ ﴿٦﴾","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[0.929411768913269,0.7764706015586853,0.556862771511078]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/KFGQPC Uthman Taha Naskh Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":12.16599178314209,"useLetterColor":true,"range":[0,39]}]}

{"text":"فَهُوَ فِى عِيشَةٍۢ رَّاضِيَةٍۢ ﴿٧﴾","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[0.929411768913269,0.7764706015586853,0.556862771511078]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/KFGQPC Uthman Taha Naskh Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":12.16599178314209,"useLetterColor":true,"range":[0,35]}]}

{"text":"وَأَمَّا مَنْ خَفَّتْ مَوَٰزِينُهُۥ ﴿٨﴾","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[0.929411768913269,0.7764706015586853,0.556862771511078]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/KFGQPC Uthman Taha Naskh Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":12.16599178314209,"useLetterColor":true,"range":[0,39]}]}

{"text":"وَمَآ أَدْرَىٰكَ مَا هِيَهْ ﴿١٠﴾","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[0.929411768913269,0.7764706015586853,0.556862771511078]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/KFGQPC Uthman Taha Naskh Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":12.16599178314209,"useLetterColor":true,"range":[0,33]}]}

{"text":"3. Al-Qori'a qandoq narsa ekanligini senga nima bildirdi?","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins-Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8.5829963684082031,"range":[0,57]}]}

{"text":"4. U kunda odamlar to`zib ketgan kapalakka \no`xshab qolarlar.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins-Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8.5829963684082031,"range":[0,61]}]}

{"text":"10. U (Haaviya) qandoq narsa ekanligini senga nima bildirdi?","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins-Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8.5829963684082031,"range":[0,60]}]}

{"text":"بِسْمِ ٱللَّهِ ٱلرَّحْمَـٰنِ ٱلرَّحِيمِ ","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,0.74901962280273438,0.45098039507865906]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/KFGQPC Uthman Taha Naskh Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":14,"useLetterColor":true,"range":[0,40]}]}
